<I>Mon, 30 Dec 1996 14:31:46 -0500 (EST)</I><PRE>

In <A HREF="/Risks/18.71.html">RISKS-18.71</A>, Jon Handler warns of the spread of personal information on
the net, and gives the URLs of several suppliers of such information.

A  longer list is available from "The Stalker's Home Page"
&lt;<A HREF="http://pages.ripco.com:8080/~glr/stalk.html">http://pages.ripco.com:8080/~glr/stalk.html</A>&gt;  It's a rather scary
resource for finding people or information about them.

--David Wittenberg	<A HREF="mailto:dkw@cs.brandeis.edu">dkw@cs.brandeis.edu</A>

