particular make sure that you put the surname in the surname field and
not the other way round. Also do not put anything in the URL field
unless it is a link to somewhere directly relevant to the person for
whom you are creating the memorial.</LI>
<LI>Check your spelling!! (alot is <I>not</I> one word!!!)</LI>
<LI> Make sure the dates are in the format nn mmm yyyy</LI>
