</B><H2>Contents</H2><DL>
<DT><IMG SRC="/Images/redball.gif" ALT= "o"><A HREF="#subj1">
  The Case of the Broken Buoy 
</A>
<DD>
<A HREF="#subj1.1">
Matt Bishop
</A><br>
<DT><IMG SRC="/Images/redball.gif" ALT= "o"><A HREF="#subj2">
  Inaction; Buoys will be buoys; KAL 007; Malpractice 
</A>
<DD>
<A HREF="#subj2.1">
PGN
</A><br>
