     Re: getting into ATM rooms
</A>
</H3>
<address>
Eric Skinner 
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:ERS2F%UOTTAWA.BITNET@CUNYVM.CUNY.EDU">
ERS2F%UOTTAWA.BITNET@CUNYVM.CUNY.EDU
</A>&gt;
