<H3><A NAME="subj6.1">
Re:  SSN Required Disclosures -- library social security privacy
</A>
</H3>
<address>
Steve Cisler
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:well!sac@cogsci.berkeley.edu ">
well!sac@cogsci.berkeley.edu 
