<H1 ALIGN="CENTER">Visitors' Book</H1>
<A HREF="/bin/guest_book?the+VMG#last">Jump to the most recent message</A><P>
<B>Please do not post memorials here; instead use the forms
(<A HREF="http://catless.ncl.ac.uk/Obituary/remember.html">people</A>
and
<A HREF="http://catless.ncl.ac.uk/Obituary/petrem.html">pets</A>)
provided.</B></P>
<P>If you want to ask a question about using the VMG or wish to point out a correction that needs to be made, then please 
<A HREF="mailto:lindsay.Marshall@newcastle.ac.uk">send me email</A>. I
do not always get the chance ot read all of the visitors' book so I may miss
your message</P><P>
I would like to thank you for the many kind things that you
have all said about the VMG - I am glad to be of service to you.</P>
