<H1>Nautilus - an [incr tcl] browser and debugger</H1>

Nautilus provides a browser and debugger for [incr tcl] classes.  The
whole system is written in [incr tcl]. The latest beta version can be
found (tar and gzip)
<A HREF="ftp://catless.ncl.ac.uk/pub/nautilus.beta.tar.gz">here</A>.
The README file can be found 
<A HREF="ftp://catless.ncl.ac.uk/pub/nautilus.README">here</A>.
I presented a paper on Nautilus at tcl94.
Nautilus is currently undergoing a major overhaul to provide a much
better level of facility. I will be putting out a beta of this version
soon.

